vote.title: Authorize an amendment to an existing lease agreement with SOHO/Davis FG, LLC to extend the lease agreement for an additional seven-years for approximately 4,290 square feet of office space located at 11910 Greenville Avenue, Suite 100, to be used as a Building Inspection North Central District Office for the period November 1, 2022 through October 31, 2029 - Not to exceed $531,231.12 - Financing: Building Inspection Fund (subject to annual appropriations)
